1. Run from root project directory:
    "./trace showcase/input-02"

2. Time (measured on OSX with 16GB RAM, 3 GHz Intel Core i7)
    3 seconds

3. Features demonstrated
    Directional light
    Reflection
    Translation
    Scaling
    Anti-aliasing
    Skybox

The first scene I rendered using a skybox. While the sphere might appear somewhat transparent, it is actually a reflecting the face of the skybox behind the camera, giving it a sort of indirect "sky" texture.